    * [SINGA-120] Implemented GRU and BPTT (BPTTWorker)

  * Neuralnet layers
    * [SINGA-91] Add SoftmaxLayer and ArgSortLayer
    * [SINGA-106] Add dummy layer for test purpose
    * [SINGA-120] Implemented GRU and BPTT (GRULayer and OneHotLayer)

